    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Simlarni Ulash Rejimi</h2>
        <p>● RJ25 bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>NSW Gaz Datchigi RJ25 porti orqali ulanishi mumkin. Makeblock Orion-da RJ25 portidan foydalanganda, uni mos keluvchi portga ulashingiz kerak:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_gassensor_rj25.jpg" alt="NSW Gaz Datchigi RJ25 Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">

        <p>● Dupont simi bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>Dupont simidan modulni Arduino UNO asos paneliga ulash uchun foydalanilganda, uning D0 va A0 pinlarini Arduino digital va analog pinlariga quyidagicha ulash lozim:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_gassensor_dupont.jpg" alt="NSW Gaz Datchigi Dupont Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Dasturlash Bo'yicha Qo'llanma</h2>
        <p>Arduino Dasturlash</p>
        <p>Agar dastur yozish uchun Arduino dan foydalansangiz, NSW Gaz Datchigini boshqarish uchun quyidagi koddan foydalanishingiz mumkin:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-cpp">
// Arduino dastur kodi
const int gasPin = A0; // Gaz datchigi analog chiqishi
const int ledPin = 13; // LED chiqishi

void setup() {
    pinMode(gasPin, INPUT);
    pinMode(ledPin, OUTPUT);
    Serial.begin(9600);
}

void loop() {
    int gasValue = analogRead(gasPin);
    Serial.println(gasValue);
    if (gasValue > 300) {
        digitalWrite(ledPin, HIGH);
    } else {
        digitalWrite(ledPin, LOW);
    }
    delay(1000);
}
        </code></pre>
